OL,3,CStarmer: I'm not going anywhere and
OL,4,CRayner has a lot to offer
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer has said he expects
OL,7,FAngela Rayner to play a "leading role
OL,8,Fin this Labour Government" despite his
OL,9,Fformer deputy's criticism over the
OL,10,Fdirection of the party.
OL,12,FThe Prime Minister insisted the ex-
OL,13,FCabinet minister had "a lot to offer"
OL,14,Fand expressed regret about her
OL,15,Fresignation last year after a row over
OL,16,Fher underpayment of stamp duty on a
OL,17,Fnew property.
OL,26,@oD@YOUpD@ZO]uD@VOUuD@eO]
