OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774576986
OL,3,CStarmer: I'm not going anywhere and
OL,4,CRayner has a lot to offer
OL,6,FIn a high-profile intervention seen by
OL,7,Fsome as a thinly veiled leadership
OL,8,Fpitch, Ms Rayner last week attacked
OL,9,Fthe Government's immigration reforms
OL,10,Fas "un-British" and said it was
OL,11,F"running out of time" to deliver.
OL,13,FAsked whether the race was on to
OL,14,Freplace him in No 10, Sir Keir told
OL,15,FSky News' Electoral Dysfunction
OL,16,Fpodcast: "Look, let me say about
OL,17,FAngela to start with, she was a
OL,18,Ffantastic deputy Prime Minister.
OL,26,@rD@DOUrD@OO]sD@AOUsD@UO]xD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
