PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774576986
OL,3,CStarmer: I'm not going anywhere and
OL,4,CRayner has a lot to offer
OL,6,F"I was very proud of the fact that
OL,7,FAngela had come from a really
OL,8,Fchallenging start in life, to then be
OL,9,Fdeputy Prime Minister.
OL,11,F"She's got a lot to offer, and I
OL,12,Fobviously had a conversation with her
OL,13,Fon the day that she had to resign, and
OL,14,FI regret that she had to resign. It
OL,15,Fwas the right thing to do, but I
OL,16,Fregret that she had to do it.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
