PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774576986
OL,3,CStarmer: I'm not going anywhere and
OL,4,CRayner has a lot to offer
OL,6,F"And I said to her, that her
OL,7,Fcontribution to the Labour government
OL,8,Fand the Labour movement was by no
OL,9,Fmeans over. And so I do expect to see
OL,10,Fher playing a leading role in this
OL,11,FLabour government."
OL,13,FMs Rayner is widely seen as a
OL,14,Fpotential successor to the Prime
OL,15,FMinister amid rumblings of a potential
OL,16,Fleadership challenge after the May 7
OL,17,Felections as Labour's poll ratings and
OL,18,Fhis personal approval flounder.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
